'''人虱'''（英文：Pediculus humanus），是指寄生在人身上的[[虱|虱]][[种|种]]，包括两个[[亚种|亚种]]<ref>{{cite book|author=William H. Robinson|year=2005|title=Handbook of Urban Insects and Arachnids|publisher=[[Cambridge_University_Press|Cambridge University Press]]|isbn=978-0-521-81253-5|chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=aluUgDVYJ8wC&pg=PA360|pages=359–364|chapter=Phthiraptera|access-date=2021-02-27|archive-date=2019-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216030933/https://books.google.com/books?id=aluUgDVYJ8wC&pg=PA360}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|editor=Gary Mullen, Gary Richard Mullen & Lance Durden|year=2009|title=Medical and Veterinary Entomology|edition=2nd|publisher=[[Academic_Press|Academic Press]]|isbn=978-0-12-372500-4|chapter=Lice (Phthiraptera)|pages=56–79|author=Lance A. Durden & John E. Lloyd|chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=6R1v9o-uaI4C&pg=PA63|access-date=2021-02-27|archive-date=2017-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215024521/https://books.google.com/books?id=6R1v9o-uaI4C&pg=PA63}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=若即若离的虱|url=http://cdcp.gd.gov.cn/khgj/jk/content/post_1106263.html|accessdate=2021-02-27|work=|publisher=广东省疾控中心|archive-date=2021-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422171909/http://cdcp.gd.gov.cn/khgj/jk/content/post_1106263.html}}</ref>：

* [[人体虱|人体虱]]或[[体虱|体虱]]（body louse），学名''Pediculus humanus humanus；''

* [[人头虱|人头虱]]或[[头虱|头虱]]（head louse），学名''Pediculus humanus capitis''

